def dice(number_of_rolls):
    dice_rolls = []
    for _ in range(number_of_rolls):
        roll = random.randint(1, 6)
        dice_rolls.append(roll)
    return dice_rolls
# roll - run it once and go into a loop
print(dice(1))
# roll 1 - produce a number 1-6 random and print it
print(dice(1))
